      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) represents a balanced example of Munich\u2019s engineering, featuring the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers precise engagement, paired with a variable M differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis has been addressed with rear subframe reinforcement and high-durometer bushings to ensure structural rigidity. Maintenance is up to date, including a recent valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the 8,000 RPM redline is met with mechanical confidence. The suspension retains its factory-tuned damping characteristics, providing the quintessential analog feedback and turn-in response this platform is known for.",
