    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. This car has been my pride and joy, and it shows in the mechanical care it has received. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though a close inspection will reveal minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scuff on the passenger-side mirror housing\u2014typical signs of a car that has enjoyed the open road. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment with premium leather upholstery that remains supple, showing only light natural creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All electronic features, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system and navigation, function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a strict regimen of full-synthetic oil changes every 5,000 miles. We recently completed a full brake service including new pads and rotors, and the tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining. The transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears, providing a confident and responsive driving experience. Included with the sale are two sets of keys, the original owner\u2019s manual, and a folder of service receipts. This is a solid, honest vehicle ready for its next chapter.",
